    <p> For creating only text color use <b>color</b> property</p>
    <p style="color: purple"> Hello this is purple color text </p>
    
    <p> For adding color in border use the <b>border </b> element and then add color</p>
    
    <p style="border:2px solid Violet;"> this text have border with 2px and color is solid violet </p>
    
    
